I find it not trustable.
I have covid and I did three attempts with this product.
The first one was negative, the second one was unreadable because there was a red stripe across the two supposed lines, and the third one was with only the T line without the C. I am pretty sure I am not the only one in the world that find this problem, and this was not my first time to do self checks. Very disappointed
